## âœ¨ Editing Content
- **Homepage:** `content/home.md`  
- **Products:** `content/products/*.json`  
  - Each product has `title`, `price`, `description`, and `image`.  
  - Add more `.json` files to add new products (e.g., figs, peaches, raspberries).  

